<li><a href="/wiki/Cate_Blanchett" title="Cate Blanchett">Cate Blanchett</a> as Janine <i>(uncredited)</i></li>
</ul>
<dl>
<dt>London residents</dt>
</dl>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Peter_Jackson" title="Peter Jackson">Peter Jackson</a> as Father Christmas <i>(uncredited)</i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Joe_Cornish_(comedian)" title="Joe Cornish (comedian)">Joe Cornish</a> as Bob</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=Chris_Waitt&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Chris Waitt (page does not exist)">Chris Waitt</a> as Dave</li>
