<dl>
<dt>Sandford residents</dt>
</dl>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Stephen_Merchant" title="Stephen Merchant">Stephen Merchant</a> as Peter Ian Staker</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Alice_Lowe" title="Alice Lowe">Alice Lowe</a> as Tina</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/David_Bradley_(actor)" title="David Bradley (actor)">David Bradley</a> as Arthur Webley</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Anne_Reid" title="Anne Reid">Anne Reid</a> as Leslie Tiller</li>
<li>Ben McKay as Peter Cocker <i>(uncredited)</i></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Adam_Buxton" title="Adam Buxton">Adam Buxton</a> as Tim Messenger</li>
