<li><a href="/wiki/Ron_Cook" title="Ron Cook">Ron Cook</a> as George Merchant</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Edgar_Wright" title="Edgar Wright">Edgar Wright</a> as Shelf Stacker <i>(uncredited)</i></li>
